---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import InnerPageHero from "../components/InnerPageHero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Course Rehab"
  description="Course rehabilitation and conditioning at Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge Golf Club — preserving Stanley Thompson’s mountain masterpiece."
>
  <InnerPageHero
    page="course-rehab"
    eyebrow="The course"
    title="Course Rehab"
    tagline="Investing in turf, bunkers, and playability so every season meets the standard you expect in Jasper National Park."
  />
  <div class="page-prose">
    <p class="lead">
      Mountain golf demands constant care: short seasons, wildlife, elevation, and weather all shape how the course ages. Rehabilitation work keeps fairways true,
      greens fast and healthy, and the routing playing as Stanley Thompson intended.
    </p>
    <p>
      The golf operations team coordinates agronomy, drainage, and selective improvements with minimal disruption to guest play. Details of current or upcoming
      projects are shared at the Golf Clubhouse and through the pro shop when you book or check in.
    </p>
    <p>
      For questions about closures, temporary tee placements, or timing for your visit, please{" "}
      <a href="/contact-us">contact the golf team</a> or call the clubhouse during posted hours.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
